<h3><b>3. Tutorials and examples.</b></h3>

<li><a href="../tutorial/lesson_ldau.html">The lesson on DFT+U</a> shows
  how to perform a DFT+U calculation using ABINIT, and will lead to
  compute the projected DOS of NiO. Prerequisite : PAW1.</li>


<p>The reader can find somes examples in the ABINIT package in the directory /tests:
<p>- v5/Input: t08.in, t14.in, t15.in, t16.int, t19.in, t20.in, t33.in, t37.in, t38.in, t39.in, t40.in.
<p>- v7/Input: t21.in, t22.in, t44.in.

